OL,3,CEx-South Scotland MSP charged with
OL,4,C'drink-driving crash'
OL,6,FA former South Scotland MSP has been
OL,7,Fcharged with almost crashing his car
OL,8,Finto a pedestrian while more than
OL,9,Fdouble the drink-driving limit.
OL,11,FColin Smyth, 52, is accused of
OL,12,Fmounting the pavement on Edinburgh's
OL,13,FHigh Street on November 2 last year.
OL,15,FProsecutors alleged that he narrowly
OL,16,Fmissed a pedestrian and was driving at
OL,17,Fan "excessive speed" at the time.
OL,26,@yD@TO]
