PN,35202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1778080262
OL,3,CEx-South Scotland MSP charged with
OL,4,C'drink-driving crash'
OL,6,FThe charges against Smyth, who was
OL,7,Felected as a Labour MSP in 2016, claim
OL,8,Fhe collided with the electric bollards
OL,9,Foutside Edinburgh's city chambers then
OL,10,Frepeatedly exited and entered the
OL,11,Fvehicle and revved its engine.
OL,13,FIt is alleged that he was found to
OL,14,Fhave 102 milligrams of alcohol in 100
OL,15,Fmillilitres of his blood, which is
OL,16,Fmore than double the legal limit of 50
OL,17,Fmilligrams per 100 millilitres.
OL,19,FSmyth is further accused of failing to
OL,20,Freport the crash.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/4
