PN,35203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1778080262
OL,3,CEx-South Scotland MSP charged with
OL,4,C'drink-driving crash'
OL,6,FHe is not standing at Thursday's
OL,7,FHolyrood election. He was previously a
OL,8,FDumfries and Galloway councillor and
OL,9,Fgeneral secretary of the Scottish
OL,10,FLabour Party.
OL,12,FA Police Scotland spokesperson said:
OL,13,F"A 52-year-old man was arrested and
OL,14,Fcharged with road traffic offences
OL,15,Ffollowing a one-vehicle crash in High
OL,16,FStreet, Edinburgh shortly after 2.10am
OL,17,Fon Sunday, 2 November 2025."
